  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effectiveness of the OCS™ Heart to recruit, preserve and assess donor hearts
      that may not meet current standard donor heart acceptance criteria (as identified above) for
      transplantation to potentially improve donor heart utilization for transplantation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
